tool_description: The ISO Country Codes API provides access to a comprehensive list of countries along with their respective ISO 3166-2 alpha-2, alpha-3, and numeric codes. This API is designed to facilitate easy retrieval of essential country information, making it a valuable resource for developers working with geographical data.
name: ISO Country Codes
title: ISO Country Codes

api_list.name: sub-region-code
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://iso-country-codes1.p.rapidapi.com/sub-region-code"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "iso-country-codes1.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
